{{TAGDEF|EVENONLYGW|[logical]|.FALSE.}}

Description: {{TAG|EVENONLYGW}} allows to restrict the k-points in the evaluation of response functions (in {{TAG|GW calculations}}) to even values.

----

{{TAG|EVENONLYGW}}=''.TRUE.'' is only of limited use and restricts the summation to k-points with <math>n_{1}+n_{2}+n_{3}</math> being even (<math>\Gamma</math> point and from there on every second k-point included).


